        "Summary": "Euler angles. Unlike a <see cref=\"T:Rotation\">Rotation</see>, Euler angles can represent multiple revolutions (rotations) around an axis,\nbut suffer from issues like gimbal lock and lack of a defined \"up\" vector. Use <see cref=\"T:Rotation\">Rotation</see> for most cases."
      },
